<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>51</hymn_number>
<title>AN KHAMH KHAWH CH51</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Thin-phangmi, nang nih tih hin lo in, Nangmah na Bawipa cung va bochan
 tuah, Thlacam tuah, na vailam rit hmanhsehlaw, Amah nih an bawmh lai,

[C1]
   Amah nih nangmah kha an khamh khawh lai, Amah kut cu ral huhphenhnak
   a si, Amah nih nangmah kha an khamh khawh lai, Khi a si ca'h phang hlah.

[V2]
 Thinphangmi, na ral kha tam hmanhseh, Ral dohnak lei naa zuamnak
 lianhter tuah, Bawipa lianngannak he na doh ahcun, Ral-teimi na si cang.

[C2]
   Amah nih nangmah kha an khamh khawh lai, Amah kut cu ral huhphenhnak
   a si, Amah nih nangmah kha an khamh khawh lai, Khi a si ca'h phang hlah.

[V3]
 Thinphangmi, na lam a har tikah Bawipa nih tihnak in an chuahter lai,
 Bawmhnak na duh ahcun Amah naih tuah, Amah min lianhter tuah,

[C3]
   Amah nih nangmah kha an khamh khawh lai, Amah kut cu ral huhphenhnak
   a si, Amah nih nangmah kha an khamh khawh lai, Khi a si ca'h phang hlah.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
</song>